data.description: Here's your chance: ASSUMABLE 2.75% VA LOAN! Beautiful home with full bathroom and bedroom downstairs for multi-generational living. Welcome to this like-new home sitting just minutes from freeways, shopping, dining, and every other desired convenience. Enjoy the 4 bedrooms and 2.75 bathrooms that are accented by an open loft, a flex dining room or front office, a large kitchen highlighted by a giant center island and plenty of counterspace, dual use walk-in pantry for additional storage or crafting area, bright and open great room, and a massive primary retreat.  Stainless steel appliances, washer & dryer, tankless water heater, covered front porch, covered back patio, and so much are waiting for you to call this HOME!
